                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding notBefore="1800" notAfter="1860"><p>Rebound in <placeName ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000208">India</placeName> in a hybrid British-Indian style, in full, British-made straight-grained green goatskin <material>leather</material> without a flap (Type III binding per Déroche), with British-made Spanish waved dark blue shell patterned <material>marbled paper</material> pastedowns.</p>
